Text: Thanks, I have been looking for a good discography, and believe it or not. The Zune HD supports AAC! Thanks alot man.

Thanks a bunch! But, as my mp3-player doesn't seem to support AAC, have you tried ABX'ing a LAME-encoded mp3 with one of your AAC-files? I couldn't hear the difference between LAME ~128 kbps VBR and FLAC on my Sennheiser hd595 phones.
